d plasma lamotrigine levels should be monitored more closely whenever estrogen- and/or progestin-containing drugs are added to or withdrawn from therapy, and the lamotrigine dosage adjusted as necessary.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/37049/', '', 'Ezogabine, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, Ganaxolone, Vigabatrin, Mephenytoin, More', 'Nafarelin, Octreotide, Elagolix, Cetrorelix, Pasireotide, Ganirelix, Relugolix, Lanreotide, Gonadorelin, Megestrol acetate, Ulipristal, More', 1767369485);
